SELECT id, title, concat('https://idyoveanwiuwcvgxijtz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/eagle-images/', storage_path) AS imageUrl
FROM eagle_images
WHERE title ILIKE '%rainforest%'
   OR EXISTS (
       SELECT 1
       FROM unnest(tags) tag
       WHERE tag ILIKE '%rainforest%'
   )
ORDER BY created_at DESC, random()
LIMIT 3;
